our eyebrows go up with anticipation; our hearts pound with passion; and fear affects us universally with gooseflesh.

00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:22,500
And in the sense that music may express those affects it is going on,

00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:26,500
then it must indeed be a universal language.

00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:31,500
Maybe even a divine one to invoke yet another cliche.

00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:36,500
I have often thought that if it's literally true that in the beginning was the word,

00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:39,500
